900.Question: How many villages border other villages?

917.Question: How many canals intersect with lakes in the United States?

1051.Question: Which US state capital has the highest population?
1051.Query: SELECT ?capital WHERE { yago:United_States geo:hasGeometry ?usGeo . ?usGeo geo:asWKT ?usWKT . ?state rdf:type y2geoo:GADM_2ndOrder_AdministrativeUnit . ?state geo:hasGeometry ?sGeo . ?sGeo geo:asWKT ?sWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?sWKT,?usWKT)). ?state yago:hasCapital ?capital . ?capital yago:hasPopulation ?population } ORDER BY DESC(xsd:integer(?population)) LIMIT 1

1052.Question: Which States are larger than England?
1052.Query: SELECT ?state { { SELECT ?state (strdf:area(?eWKT) as ?eArea) (strdf:area(?sWKT) as ?sArea) WHERE { yago:United_States geo:hasGeometry ?usGeo . ?usGeo geo:asWKT ?usWKT . yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?eGeo . ?eGeo geo:asWKT ?eWKT . ?state rdf:type y2geoo:GADM_2ndOrder_AdministrativeUnit . ?state geo:hasGeometry ?sGeo . ?sGeo geo:asWKT ?sWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?sWKT,?usWKT)). } } FILTER(?sArea > ?eArea) .}

1053.Question: Which are the 3 largest canals, by length, in Scotland?
1053.Query: SELECT ?canal { yago:Scotland geo:hasGeometry ?eGeo . ?eGeo geo:asWKT ?eWKT . ?canal rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_canal . ?canal geo:hasGeometry ?cGeo . ?cGeo geo:asWKT ?cWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?cWKT, ?eWKT)) } ORDER BY DESC(strdf:area(?cWKT)) LIMIT 3

1054.Question: Which is the longest canal in England?
1054.Query: SELECT ?canal { yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?eGeo . ?eGeo geo:asWKT ?eWKT . ?canal rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_canal . ?canal geo:hasGeometry ?cGeo . ?cGeo geo:asWKT ?cWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?cWKT, ?eWKT)) } ORDER BY DESC(strdf:area(?cWKT)) LIMIT 1

1055.Question: Is Northern Ireland the least forested country in the UK?
1055.Query: ASK { { SELECT (SUM(strdf:area(?fccWKT)) as ?areaCC) WHERE { yago:United_Kingdom geo:hasGeometry ?ukGeo . ?ukGeo geo:asWKT ?ukWKT . ?constituentCountry rdf:type y2geoo:GADM_2ndOrder_AdministrativeUnit . ?constituentCountry geo:hasGeometry ?cGeo . ?cGeo geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?forectCC rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest . ?forectCC geo:hasGeometry ?fccGeo . ?fccGeo geo:asWKT ?fccWKT . FILTER(?constituentCountry != yago:Northern_Ireland && geof:sfWithin(?cWKT,?ukWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?fccWKT,?cWKT)) . } } { SELECT (SUM(strdf:area(?fccWKT)) as ?areaNI) WHERE { yago:Northern_Ireland geo:hasGeometry ?niGeo . ?niGeo geo:asWKT ?niWKT . ?forectNI rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest . ?forectNI geo:hasGeometry ?fniGeo . ?fniGeo geo:asWKT ?fniWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?fniWKT,?niWKT)) . } } FILTER(?areaNI < ?areaCC ) . }

1056.Question: Which is the largest lake southeast of Galway?
1056.Query: SELECT ?lake (strdf:area(?lWKT) as ?lArea) WHERE { yago:County_Galway geo:hasGeometry ?cgGeo . ?cgGeo geo:asWKT ?cgWKT . yago:Republic_of_Ireland geo:hasGeometry ?iGeo . ?iGeo geo:asWKT ?iWKT . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake . ?lake geo:hasGeometry ?lGeo . ?lGeo geo:asWKT ?lWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?lWKT,?iWKT) && strdf:below(?lWKT,?cgWKT) && strdf:right(?lWKT,?cgWKT)) } ORDER BY DESC(?lArea) LIMIT 1

1057.Question: Which is the largest park in Greece?
1057.Query: SELECT ?park (strdf:area(?pWKT) as ?area) WHERE { yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?geo . ?geo geo:asWKT ?gWKT . ?park a y2geoo:OSM_park . ?park geo:hasGeometry ?parkGeo . ?parkGeo geo:asWKT ?pWKT. FILTER (geof:sfContains(?gWKT, ?pWKT)) } ORDER BY DESC(?area) LIMIT 1

1058.Question: Is Scotland's capital also its largest city?
1058.Query: ASK { yago:Scotland yago:hasCapital ?capital. ?capital geo:hasGeometry ?cgeo . ?cgeo geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?capital y2geoo:hasGADM_NationalLevel ?cnl . ?city y2geoo:hasGADM_NationalLevel ?cnl . ?city geo:hasGeometry ?citygeo . ?citygeo geo:asWKT ?cityWKT . yago:Scotland geo:hasGeometry ?sgeo . ?sgeo geo:asWKT ?sWKT . FILTER (strdf:contains(?sWKT, ?cityWKT)) . BIND (strdf:area(?cWKT) as ?capitalArea) . BIND (strdf:area(?cityWKT) as ?cityArea) . FILTER (?cityArea > ?capitalArea) }

1059.Question: Which is the largest uninhabited island?
1059.Query: SELECT ?island { SELECT ?island (strdf:area(?iWKT) as ?iArea) { ?island rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_island . ?island geo:hasGeometry ?iGeo . ?iGeo geo:asWKT ?iWKT . OPTIONAL { ?island yago:hasPopulation ?pop . } FILTER(!bound(?pop)) . } } ORDER BY DESC(?iArea) LIMIT 1

1060.Question: Which is the smallest beach in the Peloponnese prefecture?
1060.Query: SELECT ?forest ((strdf:area(?forestWKT)) as ?forestArea) WHERE { y2geor:gadmentity_Peloponnese_GRC.7.2_1 geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?pWKT . ?forest a y2geoo:OSM_beach . ?forest geo:hasGeometry ?o3 . ?o3 geo:asWKT ?forestWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?forestWKT, ?pWKT)) } ORDER BY ASC(?forestArea) LIMIT 1

1061.Question: Which is the largest lake south of Thessaloniki and north of Athens?
1061.Query: SELECT ?lake ((strdf:area(?lakeWKT)) as ?forestArea) WHERE { yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?o5 . ?o5 geo:asWKT ?greeceWKT . yago:geoentity_Dimos_Thessaloniki_8133841 geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?thessWKT . yago:geoentity_Dimos_Athens_8133876 geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?athensWKT . ?lake a y2geoo:OSM_lake . ?lake geo:hasGeometry ?o3 . ?o3 geo:asWKT ?lakeWKT . FILTER(geof:sfContains(?greeceWKT, ?lakeWKT) && strdf:below(?lakeWKT, ?thessWKT) && strdf:above(?lakeWKT, ?athensWKT)) } ORDER BY DESC(?forestArea) LIMIT 1

1062.Question: Which is the largest beach in Greece north of Athens?
1062.Query: SELECT ?forest ((strdf:area(?forestWKT)) as ?forestArea) WHERE { yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?greeceWKT . yago:geoentity_Dimos_Athens_8133876 geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?athensWKT . ?forest a y2geoo:OSM_beach . ?forest geo:hasGeometry ?o3 . ?o3 geo:asWKT ?forestWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?forestWKT, ?greeceWKT) && strdf:above(?forestWKT, ?athensWKT)) } ORDER BY DESC(?forestArea) LIMIT 1

1063.Question: How large is the the smallest county of England?
1063.Query: SELECT (MIN(strdf:area(?cWKT)) as ?mini) WHERE { yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?eGeo . ?eGeo geo:asWKT ?eWKT . ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County . ?county geo:hasGeometry ?cGeo . ?cGeo geo:asWKT ?cWKT . FILTER (geof:sfContains(?eWKT, ?cWKT)) }

1064.Question: Which is the smallest municipality of Greece?
1064.Query: SELECT ?muni (strdf:area(?wkt) as ?area) WHERE {?muni a y2geoo:GAG_Municipality . ?muni geo:hasGeometry ?geom . ?geom geo:asWKT ?wkt . yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?o1. ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1. FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?wkt, ?geoWKT1)) } ORDER BY DESC(?area) LIMIT 1

1065.Question: Does Attica have more lakes than Crete?
1065.Query: ASK {{SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?lake1) AS ?atticaLakes) WHERE {?lake1 a y2geoo:OSM_lake .?lake1 geo:hasGeometry ?lgeom1 .?lgeom1 geo:asWKT ?lwkt1 .yago:Attica_\(region\) geo:hasGeometry ?ogeom1 .?ogeom1 geo:asWKT ?owkt1 .FILTER (geof:sfWithin(?lwkt1, ?owkt1)) .}}{SELECT (COUNT(DISTINCT ?lake2) AS ?creteLakes) WHERE {?lake2 a y2geoo:OSM_lake .?lake2 geo:hasGeometry ?lgeom2 .?lgeom2 geo:asWKT ?lwkt2 .yago:Crete geo:hasGeometry ?ogeom2 .?ogeom2 geo:asWKT ?owkt2 .FILTER (geof:sfWithin(?lwkt2, ?owkt2)) .}}FILTER (?atticaLakes > ?creteLakes)}

1066.Question: Is there at least one beach in any of the top 10 most populated municipalities in Greece?
1066.Query: ASK { { SELECT ?municipality ?munWKT ?population WHERE { ?municipality a y2geoo:GAG_Municipality . ?municipality y2geoo:hasGAG_Population ?population . ?municipality geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?munWKT . } ORDER BY DESC(?population) LIMIT 10 } ?beach a y2geoo:OSM_beach . ?beach geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?beachWKT . FILTER( geof:sfWithin(?beachWKT,?munWKT) ) }

1067.Question: Is the population of the most nothern city in Scotland less than the population of the most southern city in Scotland?
1067.Query: ASK { { SELECT ?cpop1 WHERE { yago:Scotland geo:hasGeometry ?sGeo . ?sGeo geo:asWKT ?sWKT . ?city rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_city . ?city yago:hasPopulation ?cpop1 . ?city geo:hasGeometry ?cGeo . ?cGeo geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?southCity rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_city . ?southCity geo:hasGeometry ?scGeo . ?scGeo geo:asWKT ?scWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?scWKT, ?sWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?scWKT, ?sWKT)) . FILTER NOT EXISTS { FILTER(?city != ?southCity && strdf:above(?scWKT,?cWKT)) . } } } { SELECT ?cpop2 WHERE { yago:Scotland geo:hasGeometry ?s2Geo . ?s2Geo geo:asWKT ?s2WKT . ?city2 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_city . ?city2 yago:hasPopulation ?cpop2 . ?city2 geo:hasGeometry ?c2Geo . ?c2Geo geo:asWKT ?c2WKT . ?southCity2 rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_city . ?southCity2 geo:hasGeometry ?sc2Geo . ?sc2Geo geo:asWKT ?sc2WKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?sc2WKT, ?s2WKT) && geof:sfWithin(?sc2WKT, ?s2WKT)) . FILTER NOT EXISTS { FILTER(?city2 != ?southCity2 && strdf:above(?sc2WKT,?c2WKT)) . } } } FILTER(xsd:integer(?cpop1) < xsd:integer(?cpop2)). }

1068.Question: Which are the two smallest municipalities in Greece?
1068.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?county ((strdf:area(?cWKT)) as ?totalArea) WHERE { { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:GAG_Municipality } ?county geo:hasGeometry ?geoC . ?geoC geo:asWKT ?cWKT } ORDER BY (?totalArea) LIMIT 2

1069.Question: Which are the easternmost towns of England?
1069.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?town WHERE { yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?eGeo . ?eGeo geo:asWKT ?eWKT . ?town rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_town . ?town geo:hasGeometry ?tGeo . ?tGeo geo:asWKT ?tWKT . ?westernTown rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_town . ?westernTown geo:hasGeometry ?wGeo . ?wGeo geo:asWKT ?wWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?tWKT, ?eWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?wWKT, ?eWKT) ). FILTER NOT EXISTS { FILTER(?town!= ?westernTown && strdf:right(?wWKT,?tWKT)) . } }

1070.Question: Which English district has the most lakes?
1070.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?district WHERE { ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake . ?village geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?district rdf:type y2geoo:OS_District . ?district geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 . FILTER (strdf:within(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT2)) } GROUP BY ?district ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?village)) LIMIT 1

1071.Question: Which county of Ireland has the most nature reserves?
1071.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?county WHERE { ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_nature_reserve . ?lake geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_County_Council . } UNION { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_City_and_County_Council. } . ?county geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 . FILTER (strdf:within(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT2)) } GROUP BY ?county ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?lake)) LIMIT 1

1072.Question: Which district of the United Kingdom has the most villages?
1072.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?district WHERE { ?village rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_village . ?village geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?district rdf:type y2geoo:OS_District . ?district geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 . FILTER (strdf:within(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT2)) } GROUP BY ?district ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?village)) LIMIT 1

1073.Question: Which Irish county has the highest number of lakes?
1073.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?county WHERE { ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake; geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_County_Council . } UNION { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_City_and_County_Council. } . ?county geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . FILTER (strdf:within(?geoWKT, ?geoWKT1)) } GROUP BY ?county ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?lake)) LIMIT 1

1074.Question: Which island of Greece has the most beaches?
1074.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?island WHERE { yago:Greece geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . ?island rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_island; geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?beach rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_beach; geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 . FILTER (strdf:within(?geoWKT1, ?geoWKT) && strdf:within(?geoWKT2, ?geoWKT1)) } GROUP BY ?island ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?beach)) LIMIT 1

1075.Question: Which county in England has the largest number of lakes?
1075.Query: select distinct ?county where { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County . ?county geo:hasGeometry ?geomLC. ?geomLC geo:asWKT ?lcnWKT. ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake. ?lake geo:hasGeometry ?geomL. ?geomL geo:asWKT ?lWKT. FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?lWKT, ?lcnWKT)) }GROUP BY (?county) ORDER BY DESC(count (?lWKT)) LIMIT 1

1076.Question: Which 5 counties of the UK have the most forests?
1076.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?county WHERE { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County . ?county geo:hasGeometry ?geoC . ?geoC geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest . ?forest geo:hasGeometry ?geoF . ?geoF geo:asWKT ?fWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?fWKT, ?cWKT)) } GROUP BY ?county ORDER BY DESC (COUNT(?forest)) LIMIT 5

1077.Question: Which county of England has the most parks?
1077.Query: SELECT ?county (COUNT(?park) as ?parkCount) WHERE { ?county a y2geoo:OS_County . ?county geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?countyWKT . ?park a y2geoo:OSM_park . ?park geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?parkWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?parkWKT , ?countyWKT)) } GROUP BY ?county ORDER BY DESC(?parkCount) LIMIT 1

1078.Question: Which barony in Ireland has the most lakes?
1078.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?barony (count (?lake) as ?numberOfLakes) where { ?barony rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Barony. ?barony geo:hasGeometry ?geomLC. ?geomLC geo:asWKT ?lcnWKT. ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_lake. ?lake geo:hasGeometry ?geomL. ?geomL geo:asWKT ?lWKT. FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?lWKT, ?lcnWKT)) }GROUP BY (?barony) ORDER BY DESC(?numberOfLakes)LIMIT 1

1079.Question: Find the 10 British Counties having the most forests.
1079.Query: SELECT ?m (COUNT(?l) AS ?count) WHERE { ?m rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County. ?m geo:hasGeometry ?mg . ?mg geo:asWKT ?mw . ?l a y2geoo:OSM_forest . ?l geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lw . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?lw,?mw)) } GROUP BY (?m) ORDER BY DESC(?count) LIMIT 10

1080.Question: Find the 10 Irish Baronies with the most forests and at least 2 lakes.
1080.Query: SELECT ?mname (COUNT(?f) AS ?count_f) WHERE { { SELECT ?mw (COUNT(?l) AS ?count_inner) WHERE { ?m rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Barony. ?m geo:hasGeometry ?mg . ?mg geo:asWKT ?mw . ?m y2geoo:hasGAG_Name ?mname. ?l a y2geoo:OSM_lake . ?l geo:hasGeometry ?lg . ?lg geo:asWKT ?lw . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?lw, ?mw)) } GROUP BY ( ?mw) } FILTER(?count_inner>1). ?f a y2geoo:OSM_forest . ?f geo:hasGeometry ?fg . ?fg geo:asWKT ?fw . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?fw,?mw)). } GROUP BY (?mname) ORDER BY DESC(?count_f) LIMIT 10

1081.Question: What is the size of the largest forest in Cambridgeshire?
1081.Query: SELECT DISTINCT (MAX(strdf:area(?geoWKT2)) AS ?maxLakeArea) WHERE { yago:Cambridge geo:hasGeometry ?o1 . ?o1 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT1 . ?lake rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest . ?lake geo:hasGeometry ?o2 . ?o2 geo:asWKT ?geoWKT2 . FILTER (strdf:within(?geoWKT2, ?geoWKT1)) }

1082.Question: How large is the largest forest in Greece?
1082.Query: SELECT (MAX(strdf:area(?forest_geoWKT)) AS ?areas_max) WHERE { <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Greece> geo:hasGeometry ?greeceGeo . ?greeceGeo geo:asWKT ?greeceWKT . ?forest rdf:type <http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/ontology/OSM_forest> . ?forest geo:hasGeometry ?forest_geo . ?forest_geo geo:asWKT ?forest_geoWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?forest_geoWKT,?greeceWKT)) }

1083.Question: What is the average area of a lake in Nevada?
1083.Query: SELECT (AVG(?areas) AS ?areas_avg) WHERE { SELECT ((strdf:area(?forest_geoWKT)) AS ?areas) WHERE { <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Nevada> geo:hasGeometry ?Cork_geo . ?Cork_geo geo:asWKT ?Cork_geoWKT . ?forest rdf:type <http://kr.di.uoa.gr/yago2geo/ontology/OSM_lake> . ?forest geo:hasGeometry ?forest_geo . ?forest_geo geo:asWKT ?forest_geoWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?forest_geoWKT,?Cork_geoWKT)) } }

1084.Question: What is the size of the largest county in the Republic of Ireland?
1084.Query: SELECT DISTINCT (MAX(strdf:area(?geoWKT)) AS ?maxArea) WHERE { { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_County_Council . } UNION { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_City_and_County_Council. } . ?county geo:hasGeometry ?o . ?o geo:asWKT ?geoWKT . }

1085.Question: Which county has the most townlands in Ireland?
1085.Query: SELECT DISTINCT ?county (COUNT(?town) AS ?num) WHERE { { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_County_Council . } UNION { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_City_and_County_Council. } . ?town rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_Townland . ?county geo:hasGeometry ?geoc . ?geoc geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?town geo:hasGeometry ?geot . ?geot geo:asWKT ?tWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?tWKT, ?cWKT)) } GROUP BY ?county ORDER BY DESC(?num) LIMIT 1

1086.Question: Which Texan county has the most lakes?
1086.Query: SELECT ?county (COUNT(?lake) AS ?lakeCount) WHERE { ?county y2geoo:hasGADM_Description "County" .?county geo:hasGeometry ?countyGeom .?countyGeom geo:asWKT ?countyWKT . yago:Texas geo:hasGeometry ?tGeom. ?tGeom geo:asWKT ?texasWKT. FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?countyWKT, ?texasWKT)) . ?lake a y2geoo:OSM_lake . ?lake geo:hasGeometry ?lakeGeom . ?lakeGeom geo:asWKT ?lakeWkt . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(strdf:buffer(?lakeWkt, 0, uom:metre), strdf:buffer(?countyWKT, 0, uom:metre))) } GROUP BY ?county ORDER BY DESC(?lakeCount) LIMIT 1

1087.Question: Does Texas have more counties than Alabama?
1087.Query: ASK { { SELECT (COUNT(?texanCounty) as ?texanCounties){ yago:Texas geo:hasGeometry ?tGeo . ?tGeo geo:asWKT ?tWKT . ?texanCounty rdf:type y2geoo:GADM_3rdOrder_AdministrativeUnit . ?texanCounty geo:hasGeometry ?tcGeo . ?tcGeo geo:asWKT ?tcWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?tcWKT,?tWKT)) . } } { SELECT (COUNT(?alabamaCounty) as ?alabamaCounties){ yago:Alabama geo:hasGeometry ?aGeo . ?aGeo geo:asWKT ?aWKT . ?alabamaCounty rdf:type y2geoo:GADM_3rdOrder_AdministrativeUnit . ?alabamaCounty geo:hasGeometry ?acGeo . ?acGeo geo:asWKT ?acWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?acWKT,?aWKT)) . } } FILTER(?texanCounties > ?alabamaCounties). }

1088.Question: How many counties of Texas are larger than Austin?
1088.Query: SELECT (COUNT(?county) as ?count) WHERE { { SELECT ?county (strdf:area(?countyWKT) AS ?county_area) (strdf:area(?austinWKT) AS ?austin_area) WHERE { ?county y2geoo:hasGADM_Description "County" ; geo:hasGeometry ?countyGeom . ?countyGeom geo:asWKT ?countyWKT . yago:Texas geo:hasGeometry ?tGeom . ?tGeom geo:asWKT ?texasWKT . <http://yago-knowledge.org/resource/Austin_County,_Texas> geo:hasGeometry ?aGeom . ?aGeom geo:asWKT ?austinWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?countyWKT,?texasWKT)) . } } FILTER(?county_area > ?austin_area)}

1089.Question: Which state in the US has the most neighboring states?
1089.Query: SELECT ?state WHERE { yago:United_States geo:hasGeometry ?usGeo . ?usGeo geo:asWKT ?usWKT . ?state rdf:type y2geoo:GADM_2ndOrder_AdministrativeUnit . ?state geo:hasGeometry ?sGeo . ?sGeo geo:asWKT ?sWKT . ?s2 rdf:type y2geoo:GADM_2ndOrder_AdministrativeUnit . ?s2 geo:hasGeometry ?s2Geo . ?s2Geo geo:asWKT ?s2WKT . FILTER(?state != ?s2 && geof:sfWithin(?sWKT,?usWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?s2WKT,?usWKT) && geof:sfTouches(?sWKT,?s2WKT)) } GROUP BY ?state ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?s2)) LIMIT 1

1090.Question: How many counties border the largest county of the Republic of Ireland?
1090.Query: SELECT (COUNT(?county) as ?counties) { { SELECT ?largestCounty ?lcWKT WHERE { { ?largestCounty rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_County_Council . } UNION { ?largestCounty rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_City_and_County_Council. } ?largestCounty geo:hasGeometry ?lcGeo . ?lcGeo geo:asWKT ?lcWKT . BIND(strdf:area(?lcWKT) as ?lcArea) . } ORDER BY DESC(?lcArea) LIMIT 1 } { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_County_Council . } UNION { ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OSI_City_and_County_Council. } ?county geo:hasGeometry ?cGeo . ?cGeo geo:asWKT ?cWKT . FILTER(geof:sfTouches(?cWKT,?lcWKT)) . }

1091.Question: Which English county has the most forests?
1091.Query: SELECT ?county { yago:England geo:hasGeometry ?eGeo . ?eGeo geo:asWKT ?eWKT . ?county rdf:type y2geoo:OS_County . ?county geo:hasGeometry ?cGeo . ?cGeo geo:asWKT ?cWKT . ?forest rdf:type y2geoo:OSM_forest . ?forest geo:hasGeometry ?fGeo . ?fGeo geo:asWKT ?fWKT . FILTER(geof:sfWithin(?cWKT,?eWKT) && geof:sfWithin(?fWKT,?cWKT)) . } GROUP BY (?county) ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?forest)) LIMIT 1

1212.Query: SELECT (SUM(xsd:integer(?pop)) as ?totalpop) WHERE { { SELECT ?city (strdf:area(?lWKT) as ?area) WHERE { yago:United_Kingdom geo:hasGeometry ?geom . ?geom geo:asWKT ?mWKT . ?lake a y2geoo:OSM_city . ?lake geo:hasGeometry ?geol . ?geol geo:asWKT ?lWKT . FILTER (geof:sfContains(?mWKT, ?lWKT)) } ORDER BY DESC(xsd:integer(?area)) LIMIT 5 } ?city yago:hasPopulation ?pop. }

1213.Question: What is the population total of the 5 largest US states?
1213.Query: SELECT (SUM(xsd:integer(?pop)) AS ?populationTotal) WHERE {SELECT ?state ?pop WHERE { ?state a yago:wikicategory_States_of_the_United_States. ?state yago:hasPopulation ?pop.} ORDER BY DESC(xsd:integer (?pop)) LIMIT 5}

1214.Question: Which city in California has the most hospitals?
1214.Query: SELECT ?city WHERE { ?type rdfs:subClassOf+ yago:wordnet_administrative_district_108491826. ?city a ?type . ?city yago:isLocatedIn+ yago:California . ?type1 rdfs:subClassOf+ yago:wordnet_hospital_103540595. ?hospital a ?type1 . ?hospital yago:isLocatedIn+ ?city.} GROUP BY ?city ORDER BY DESC(COUNT(?hospital)) LIMIT 1
